[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1214","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1214.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0870","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在文件上传控件中粘贴文件名的方式，利用不可信脚本粘贴功能读取目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4.01 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，可能导致敏感信息泄露。由于该漏洞利用条件简单，仅需诱导用户访问恶意网页即可触发，具有较大的实际威胁。Microsoft 已在后续版本中修复此问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0870"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.733","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。对于仍使用 IE 4.01 的遗留系统，建议禁用 Active Scripting 功能，在 Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别中将「脚本」设置为禁用，或迁移至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-015","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0870.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0870","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0870.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0870.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cjf6-94c6-7rc2/GHSA-cjf6-94c6-7rc2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0870.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88084/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000371.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1214.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1214.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0810","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0546","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 默认启用访客账户权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 操作系统默认启用 guest（来宾）账户，该账户无需密码即可通过网络登录系统。攻击者可利用该漏洞以 guest 身份远程登录目标系统，访问共享文件、打印机等网络资源，获取系统信息或进行进一步探测。此漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。尽管 guest 账户权限受限，但不当配置可能导致信息泄露或作为攻击跳板。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0546"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.500","remediation":"立即禁用 Windows NT/2000 系统中的 Guest 账户：通过「计算机管理」→「本地用户和组」→「用户」，右键单击 Guest 账户选择「属性」，勾选「账户已禁用」。若系统未安装安全策略管理工具，可使用命令行执行 `net user Guest /active:no` 禁用该账户。同时建议在本地安全策略中配置「账户：来宾账户状态」为「已禁用」，并确保来宾账户不属于任何具有敏感权限的用户组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0546","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0546.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7427eace1f860911aaff217b01d8aca088243b9f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0546.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0546","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0546.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0546.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w5j7-6c9r-vm95/GHSA-w5j7-6c9r-vm95.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0546.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87877/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0760","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0506","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9111,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 的域用户或管理员账户存在默认密码为空（null）、空白（blank）或缺失（missing）的安全缺陷。该漏洞源于系统在初始配置时未强制为域账户设置强密码，导致攻击者可在无需任何凭证的情况下直接利用空密码远程或本地登录目标域账户。影响范围涵盖运行 Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 的域控制器及加入域的计算机，危害等级较高（CVSS 7.2）。攻击条件为：目标主机开启了域账户登录且相关账户未配置密码。利用方式简单，攻击者可凭空密码直接进行身份认证，进而获取域用户乃至管理员权限，造成信息泄露、权限提升与进一步横向移动的风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0506"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.433","remediation":"为所有 Windows NT/2000 域用户和管理员帐户设置强密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符）。通过域安全策略启用密码复杂性要求，开启「密码必须满足复杂性要求」和「密码长度最小值」，并禁用「允许使用空白密码的帐户只允许控制台登录」策略。在本地安全策略中将「帐户: 使用空白密码的本地帐户只允许进行控制台登录」设置为已启用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0506","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0506.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0506","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0506.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0506.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/907ae4099f60f85a9473cd7e47129d370c445f83/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p477-22hv-c2xc/GHSA-p477-22hv-c2xc.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login_as_users.nasl","https://github.com/pentestmonkey/yaptest/blob/9ec017c3bba687c66d94693020c7a0b45e265ae2/metasploit-exploit-suggest.pl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0759","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0759.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0505","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 域用户及管理员账户弱口令漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，域用户或管理员账户使用了过于简单、可被轻易猜测的口令。攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击方式，远程或本地尝试登录目标系统的域控制器或成员服务器，成功后可获取该账户的访问权限，进而可能提升至域管理员权限，控制整个 Windows 域环境。该漏洞影响所有未实施强口令策略的 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 域环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0505"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.317","remediation":"在域安全策略中启用密码必须符合复杂性要求并设置最小长度≥8位；通过组策略配置账户锁定阈值（5次无效登录锁定30分钟）；升级至Windows Server 2003以上版本以增强Kerberos认证；立即排查并重置所有域管理员账户的弱密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0505","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0505.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0505","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/bbd7116272e853f39577ba54522637fe18ed9411/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0505.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smb_guest_account.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83215/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0759.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0369","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0186","title":"Sun Solaris SNMP 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 SNMP 子代理程序存在默认团体字符串（community string）漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 SNMP 协议访问目标系统，利用该默认字符串执行任意命令获取 root 权限，或修改系统关键参数。此漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统多个版本，攻击门槛低且危害极高，CVSS 评分 10.0，属于严重级别。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0186"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.033","remediation":"立即修改 SNMP 默认 community string，将 snmpd.conf 中默认的 \"public\" 改为自定义复杂字符串；升级 Solaris 至包含补丁 105230-xx (Solaris 2.5/2.5.1) 或 105231-xx (Solaris 2.4) 及更高版本；如无需 SNMP 子代理功能，禁用 snmpdx 守护进程；在防火墙层面限制 UDP 161 端口仅对可信管理站开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.novell.com/cgi-bin/search/searchtid.cgi?/10080762.htm","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-238/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1253","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0969","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RPC 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 RPC 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞（Snork），远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的伪造畸形 RPC 数据包触发错误响应，该响应被发送回伪造源地址，形成循环反射放大攻击，导致目标系统 RPC 服务崩溃或资源耗尽。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0969"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.843","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-014 提供的补丁程序，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在防火墙层面过滤 UDP 135、137、138、445 端口及 TCP 135、139、445 端口，阻止外部未授权 RPC 流量访问。同时限制匿名用户对 RPC 服务的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ193233","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-014","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0969","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/51bb5d1dd73018638fab64f7b55edb2ba6e6a124/1999/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/554ca72965233bd9402be197b5470aad836fe056/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-09xx/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0969.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0969.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1379","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1379.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1181","title":"Silicon Graphics IRIX 在线客户注册软件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Silicon Graphics IRIX 6.2 至 6.4 操作系统中的在线客户注册软件（On-Line Customer Registration）存在本地权限提升漏洞。该软件在处理用户操作时权限校验不当，导致拥有本地登录权限的普通用户可利用该缺陷提升至 root 权限，从而完全控制目标系统。攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，无需身份认证即可触发，影响机密性、完整性和可用性。该漏洞影响所有运行 IRIX 6.2、6.3 及 6.4 版本的 SGI 工作站与服务器，攻击者成功利用后可读取、篡改任意文件并执行任意管理命令，是导致系统被本地完全接管的高危风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1181"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-29","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"SGI 已在安全公告 19980901-01-PX 中发布补丁，建议从 patches.sgi.com 下载并安装对应 IRIX 6.2/6.3/6.4 的官方补丁，或升级至 IRIX 6.5 及以上版本以彻底修复。若暂无法打补丁，可移除或禁用在线客户注册软件相关的 setuid 程序，并限制普通用户对注册组件的访问权限以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["ftp://patches.sgi.com/support/free/security/advisories/19980901-01-PX","http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-003.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7441.php","https://cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-1181","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1181"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1379.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1415","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1415.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1228","title":"多厂商调制解调器 AT 命令远程代码执行漏洞","description":"某些调制解调器未实现或配置了零秒的防护时间（Guard Time），导致攻击者可将 Hayes 命令集转义序列 \"+++\" 嵌入 ICMP 数据包、电子邮件主题、IRC 消息等网络流量中，远程触发调制解调器执行 ATH、ATH0 等任意 AT 命令。该漏洞影响多款未启用防护时间的调制解调器设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。受影响的设备默认不具备防护机制，数据流中的普通字符序列即可被误解析为命令转义序列，造成未授权的调制解调器操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1228"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.507","remediation":"将调制解调器的 S12 寄存器（逃逸序列保护时间）设置为非零值，推荐设为 10（即 1 秒保护时间），通过 AT 指令 `ATS12=10` 写入并保存。该配置要求 `+++` 序列前后必须有至少 1 秒的空闲时间，可有效防止来自邮件正文、ICMP 报文等数据流中的误触发。如果调制解调器不支持 S12 配置，应升级固件或替换为支持保护间隔的型号。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90695973308453&w=2","http://www.macintouch.com/modemsecurity.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3320","https://github.com/mthcht/awesome-lists/blob/6db6e342a39ebfac0cb9495ba1bcabdd588e5fc8/Lists/Others/Defender_yara_rules/Linux/Exploit/CVE-1999-1228.yara","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1228.json","https://github.com/roadwy/DefenderYara/blob/59e39903d9e6667c7c3e55a1f2887f1faab0e423/Exploit/Linux/CVE-1999-1228/Exploit_Linux_CVE-1999-1228_A_xp.yar","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1228","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1228.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1228.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqv9-mm7j-xwfh/GHSA-xqv9-mm7j-xwfh.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/petikvx/VirusShare_ELF/blob/d7c50d4e58f7548429da993c743efe8a9f3e0fee/TREEMALWARE"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1415.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1307","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1307.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1054","title":"FLEXlm许可管理器远程服务器关闭漏洞","description":"FLEXlm许可证管理器（如6.0d版本）的默认配置存在严重的安全缺陷。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送包含lmdown命令的特制数据包，向目标FLEXlm许可服务器发起关闭请求。由于该命令的认证机制仅基于客户端自称具有root权限的信任模型，攻击者只需构造符合协议格式的请求报文，即可远程终止许可证管理服务，造成合法用户无法获取授权，进而导致依赖该许可的软件产品无法正常运行。该漏洞影响运行FLEXlm许可证管理器的各类工程软件、CAD工具及商业应用程序服务器，攻击者无需获取目标系统权限即可实现服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1054"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.637","remediation":"升级 FLEXlm 许可管理器至 7.0 及以上版本（建议 11.x 最新版）。在新版中编辑许可服务配置文件，移除或不授予 `lmdown` 权限（使用 `lmgrd -z` 禁止远程关闭，或在 options 文件中删除 ADMIN 对应的关闭权限），并将 lmgrd 监听端口（默认 27000-27009）通过防火墙限制为仅允许可信内网 IP 访问，禁止公网直接连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90675672323825&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1054.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1054","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1054.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2d0833866f347223eab80ef68cc3e2461a4e724d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1054.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xxf6-r989-348x/GHSA-xxf6-r989-348x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1054.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88502/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5490498c-71c5-40a2-8992-ceaa9e54be84.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/1216817b1ffea775aa09a87ad4eb5d4ec3f12b57/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1307.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1434","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1434.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1265","title":"Seattle Lab Software SLmail SMTP 命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Seattle Lab Software 出品的 SLmail 3.1 及更早版本的 SMTP 服务组件存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标 SMTP 端口发送参数以左括号 \"(\" 开头的畸形命令（如 SEND、VRFY、EXPN、MAIL FROM、RCPT TO）触发该漏洞，导致邮件服务进程崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SLmail 3.1 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1265"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.197","remediation":"升级到 SLmail 4.0 或更高版本（该漏洞在后续版本中已修复）。由于 SLmail 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Exchange Server、Postfix 等）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制对 TCP 端口 25 的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接 SMTP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90649892424117&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90650438826447&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1664","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1265.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1265","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1265.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1265.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68wf-hv6w-35mw/GHSA-68wf-hv6w-35mw.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87811/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1265.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1434.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1228","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1020","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16371,\"outputTokens\":31,\"totalTokens\":16402}}","description":"Novell NetWare 4.1 及 4.11（含 SP5B 补丁）在安装 NDS（Novell Directory Services）5.99 版本时，默认赋予未认证客户端对整个目录树的读取（Read）权限。远程攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，即可利用系统自带的 CX.EXE 与 NLIST.EXE 等工具连接目标目录树，枚举并读取其中的用户、用户组及其他可读对象等敏感信息。该漏洞影响所有部署了 NDS 5.99 的 Novell NetWare 4.1/4.11 服务器，攻击者仅需网络可达目标服务端口并能运行上述客户端工具即可实施信息泄露，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1020"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.213","remediation":"建议升级至 Novell NetWare 5.0 或更高版本（已停止支持），或应用 Novell 发布的 NDS 修补程序（如 NW411SP6A.EXE 及后续补丁）。若无法升级，建议通过防火墙限制 524/TCP 端口仅允许受信任管理网段访问，禁用 CX.EXE 和 NLIST.EXE 客户端工具的网络访问权限，并配置 NDS ACL 移除 [Public] 对树对象的 [Read] 权限，仅授权管理员账户访问敏感对象属性。建议尽快迁移至现代目录服务（如 Microsoft Active Directory 或 OpenLDAP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90613355902262&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/484","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1364","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1020.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1020","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1020.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1020.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q937-qhpq-5w36/GHSA-q937-qhpq-5w36.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/nds_web_based_browsing.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1020.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/484/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0147","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0147.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0056","title":"Sun Solaris ping 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 ping 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户通过向 ping 程序提交特制参数可触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.x 及 Solaris 2.x 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。攻击者需拥有本地系统普通用户权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0056"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.453","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方提供的对应补丁（如 SunOS 5.x 和 Solaris 2.x 的推荐安全补丁集）。如无法打补丁，可临时移除 ping 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ping），以消除本地提权风险。建议升级至不受影响的 Solaris 版本或迁移至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/174"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0147.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1220","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1220.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0897","title":"iChat ROOMS Webserver 目录遍历漏洞","description":"iChat ROOMS Webserver 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 路径中使用 ../ 序列绕过访问限制，读取服务器上任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，可导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0897"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-09-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该漏洞源于 iChat ROOMS Webserver 对用户输入路径过滤不严，攻击者可通过 ../ 序列遍历目录读取任意文件。由于该产品已停止维护且无官方补丁，建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器软件（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx），并在应用层对用户请求路径进行规范化校验，拒绝包含 ../ 或空字节等特殊字符的请求。同时配置 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）规则拦截目录遍历攻击模式作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90538488231977&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1220.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1305","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1305.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1048","title":"GNU Bash 提示符目录名处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"GNU Bash 在某个版本中存在缺陷，当使用包含 \\w（当前工作目录）的 PS1 提示符变量时，若当前目录名称异常长（例如用户切换到一个超大目录名），bash 会错误地处理该目录名并在生成密码提示符时发生拒绝服务，导致 shell 挂起或消耗大量资源而无法正常响应。攻击者在共享或多用户环境中可构造超长目录名诱导受害者进入，从而使其交互式 shell 不可用。该漏洞影响本地交互场景，需受害者处于该异常目录下方可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1048"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-05","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 bash 至修复该缺陷的 2.0.1 及以上版本（Debian 用户执行 apt-get update && apt-get install bash）。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/profile 及用户配置中将 PS1 中的 \\w 改为 \\W 或直接移除 \\w 选项，避免将超大目录名插入密码提示，并限制普通用户对公共目录的写权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602746719555&w=2","http://www.debian.org/security/1998/19980909","http://www.osvdb.org/8345","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10542","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3414"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1305.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1217","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0871","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨帧导航信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 及 4.01 版本存在跨帧安全漏洞（Cross Frame Navigate），远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用浏览器跨帧导航机制绕过同源策略限制，读取目标用户本地文件系统中的敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 IE 4.0/4.01 版本，攻击者需诱使用户访问恶意网站，无需身份认证即可实施攻击，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0871"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.867","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 及以上版本，或改用 Microsoft Edge/Chrome/Firefox 等现代浏览器。IE 4.0 已停止支持且存在大量未修复漏洞，不应继续使用。如因兼容性必须使用旧版 IE，建议启用 Internet Explorer 增强安全配置并禁用 ActiveX 脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7837","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-013","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3668","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9